00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:24,820
If you can't bring results in a month, there will be consequences.

151
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:25,930
Don't worry.

152
00:11:25,930 --> 00:11:28,610
I'll make sure to keep my word.

153
00:11:28,610 --> 00:11:30,600
I'll look forward to it.

154
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:33,500
- You can leave now. 
 - Okay.

155
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:42,490
Do you still have something to say?

156
00:11:42,490 --> 00:11:45,290
As a present from your business trip,

157
00:11:45,290 --> 00:11:48,870
