235
00:18:21,130 --> 00:18:23,810
Gosh, this is driving me crazy.

236
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:26,880
I need to finish my mission to go back.

237
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:32,300
And I need to know how to go back to decide if I will or not.

238
00:18:32,300 --> 00:18:34,180
Seriously...

239
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:50,470
What's this?

240
00:19:35,150 --> 00:19:37,230
- Hello? 
  - Buongiorno. 

241
00:19:37,230 --> 00:19:39,510
Are you joking right now?

242
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:41,780
Gosh, how scary. I thought you were a tiger.

243
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:44,620
Well, what made you so angry?

244
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,500
How could I not be angry right now?

245
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:49,530
