247
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:54,500
Okay, okay. Calm down. Let's talk it over calmly.

248
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,040
Talk it over, my foot.

249
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:58,530
 You'll say cryptic things, anyway. 

250
00:19:58,530 --> 00:20:01,940
